title: VA Indie Lo-Fi Folk Sept 2013 - Friend Like You (Dutch Treat I1
description:
Already the fourth Indie playlist from September 2013 and yet again another I1 list. Very Beautiful and very very easy. So do not expect noise.

Thanks to my imaginary "Best Indie" friend, I had a very nice weekend. It's nice to meet an idiot like myself. Some recognition maybe. Anyway we listened to some thousand songs. Most were beautiful, some clearly good and some were just to good to keep quiet. So I put these songs in my September lists (although most of them are a bit older but you might have missed them too). But whatever reason; in my ears, the list is quite special as it is. The songs really support each other. All in XHQ..... Enjoy,
